text: All That Jazz is a 1979 American musical drama movie directed by Bob Fosse and starring Roy Scheider, Jessica Lange, Leland Palmer, Ann Reinking, Cliff Gorman, John Lithgow, Anthony Holland, C. C. H. Pounder and Wallace Shawn. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox and was nominated for 9 Oscars and won 4 Oscars at the Academy Awards in 1980. In 2001, the Library of Congress selected All That Jazz into the United States National Film Registry. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1979 drama movies Category:1970s American drama movies Category:Movies directed by Bob Fosse Category:1970s American musical movies Category:1970s English-language movies Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies set in New York City Category:Academy Award winning movies Category:United States National Film Registry movies
